<i>adverb</i>: 훌렁 [훌렁], 훌러덩 [훌러덩], 호락호락 [호라코락], 슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍], 슬쩍 [슬쩍], 슬슬 [슬슬], 살짝 [살짝], 반짝 [반짝], 간단히 [간단히], 가벼이 [가벼이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훌렁 [훌렁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. completely; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>속이 시원하게 드러나도록 완전히 벗어지거나 뒤집히는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of something being completely taken off or turned inside out so that the inside is clearly exposed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. completely; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>가지고 있던 돈이나 재산 등을 다 날려 버리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of losing all of one's money or wealth, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. loosely; in a slippery manner</dd><br>
<dd>구멍이 넓어서 아주 헐겁게 빠지거나 들어가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of slipping out easily or fitting loosely because the hole is wide.</dd><br>
<dd>4. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 쉽게 뛰어넘거나 들어 올리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of jumping across or lifting something very easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훌러덩 [훌러덩]</dt><br>
<dd>1. completely; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>속이 시원하게 드러나도록 완전히 벗어지거나 뒤집히는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of something being completely taken off or turned inside out so that the inside is clearly exposed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. completely; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>가지고 있던 돈이나 재산 등을 다 날려 버리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of losing all of one's money or wealth, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 쉽게 뛰어넘거나 들어 올리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of jumping across or lifting something very easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호락호락 [호라코락]</dt><br>
<dd>easily; without difficulty; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 사람이 만만하여 다루기 쉬운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a task or person being pliable enough to be easily managed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and lightly without much effort..</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quietly so that others do not know..</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 잇따라 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession, carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>슬쩍 [슬쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>Carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>슬슬 [슬슬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slowly</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 천천히 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly, not hastening.</dd><br>
<dd>8. effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘들이지 않고 쉽게 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing something easily without much effort.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살짝 [살짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반짝 [반짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>물건을 한 번에 아주 가볍게 들어 올리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of lifting something without difficulty.</dd><br>
<dd>2. aloft</dd><br>
<dd>물건의 끝이 갑자기 아주 높이 들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that the edge of something is suddenly lifted very high.</dd><br>
<dd>3. high and lightly</dd><br>
<dd>몸의 한 부분을 갑자기 가볍게 위로 들어 올리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of lifting a part of one's body lightly and suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. all of a sudden</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 눈을 크게 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of suddenly opening one's eyes wide.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>간단히 [간단히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>길거나 복잡하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that does not make something lengthy or complicated.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lighlty; little</dd><br>
<dd>번거롭거나 많지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that does not cause much trouble or require too many things.</dd><br>
<dd>3. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>다루거나 하기가 꽤 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that makes something easy to handle or do.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가벼이 [가벼이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>무게를 적게.</dd><br>
<dd>With little weight.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly; rashly</dd><br>
<dd>맡은 일의 비중이나 가치, 책임 등이 낮거나 적게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the importance, value, responsibility, etc., of one's given task is low or less.</dd><br>
<dd>3. lightly; slightly</dd><br>
<dd>죄나 실수, 손해 등이 심하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that a crime, mistake, damage, etc., is not serious.</dd><br>
<dd>4. rashly; indiscreetly</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 말, 행동이 진지하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one's thinking, speech or behavior is not serious.</dd><br>
<dd>5. lightly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>부담이 되지 않도록 간단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the action does not become a burden.</dd><br>
<dd>6. lightly; easily</dd><br>
<dd>대수롭지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one considers something easy.</dd><br>
<dd>7. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 들지 않고 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without trouble or effort.</dd><br>
<dd>8. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>일렁이거나 흔들리는 정도가 약하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the degree of wavering or swaying is weak.</dd><br>
<dd>9. simply</dd><br>
<dd>옷차림이나 화장이 요란하지 않고 활동하기에 편하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the clothes and make-up are not too dressy but are instead comfortable for activities.</dd><br>
<dd>10. easily; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>몸의 움직임이 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the movement of the body is quick.</dd><br>
<dd>11. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 편하고 경쾌하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the mind is comfortable and joyful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>